  <name>KDE SIP Client</name>
  <summary>Modern SIP softphone for KDE Plasma</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      KDE SIP Client is a native, high-performance SIP softphone built specifically for
      KDE Plasma desktop environment. It provides a modern, beautiful interface while
      delivering exceptional performance and stability.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full SIP protocol support (UDP/TCP/TLS)</li>
      <li>SRTP encryption for secure calls</li>
      <li>PipeWire native audio integration</li>
      <li>Multiple account support</li>
      <li>Call transfer, hold, and conferencing</li>
      <li>DTMF support (RFC 2833 and SIP INFO)</li>
      <li>KWallet integration for secure credential storage</li>
      <li>Native Plasma notifications</li>
      <li>System tray integration</li>
      <li>Follows KDE HIG and theme system</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

